profile: Benedetti Orthodontics prides itself on creating the most amazing smiles of today with the technology of tomorrow. By giving patients the best customer service possible combined with the most up to date treatment techniques, Dr. Benedetti is able to give patients the smile they have always dreamed of. Dr. Ana Benedetti grew up in South Florida, with a Brazilian heritage and her academic credentials are stellar! She graduated from the University of Miami, Magna cum Laude, with degrees in Biology and Spanish, and then pursued her dental training from the University of Florida - School of Dentistry. She was excited to have the opportunity to continue her training at the prestigious Medical College of Virginia where she obtained her certificate in Orthodontics as well as her Master of Science in Dentistry.
name: Benedetti Orthodontics
